% ====================================================================
% test_bestagon_proto_pathfind.trx -- run examples/bestagon-proto/
% proto-pathfind.trx via the tests/ harness.
% ====================================================================
%
% Thin wrapper: loads proto-pathfind.trx (Phase 0.6G: reachable-hexes
% with terrain + ZOC + impassable + indirect-fire range bracket-check
% per GDD sections 4 + 7.7 + 7.9).
%
% 20 assertions across 5 sections:
%   A: clear 7x7 plain, Tank at [3,3] move=6 covers all 49 cells
%   B: corridor map, ZOC halt + mountain walls block east-of-enemy
%   C: Mountain at [4,3] impassable to Tank (tread class)
%   D: indirect-range-ok? bracket-check for Artillery 2-3 + Rocket 3-5
%   E: section 7.9 Phase 5 invariant -- Recon halts on enter-ZOC
%
% Throws on any assertion mismatch.  Runs on default 1 MB VM in < 1 s.
% ====================================================================

(examples/bestagon-proto/proto-pathfind.trx) run
(__test_ok__) =
